reviewText: Haven't had a chance to watch this yet, but I know the movies on it and I love them.
I haven't watched them all but the price is certainly right for so many fun films.  I love the movie "Speechless."
Could barely watch Speechless, and probably will never watch Real Men or Making Mr. Right.  But worth the price to try them all.

I ordered this product because for the 6 movies mentioned at this price, how could it not be worth it. Only thing is, The Woman in Red is not one of the 6 movies that came in the package, but Baby Boom with Diane Keaton did. Still a fantastic 6 pack no matter how you look at, so completely satisfied!

Now that we've switched over to DVD (from VHS tapes) I find I am running out of shelf space and need to economize with my DVD selections. This package contains 6 excellent movies yet takes up very little shelf space. These are 6 comedies that make for excellent evening entertainment for 6 nights straight... can't beat that!

I bought the package because I saw a little bit of "Overboard" on TV and wanted to have the whole movie on a DVD. Two of the other movies were good, so I got more than my money's worth from the purchase.
